commit message:
Updated README

Bump version # to correct version and add some of the new features to the feature list.

Merge branch 'master' into guide-completions

Conflicts:
App/res/values/strings.xml
App/src/com/dozuki/ifixit/model/guide/Guide.java
App/src/com/dozuki/ifixit/ui/guide/view/GuideViewActivity.java
App/src/com/dozuki/ifixit/util/JSONHelper.java

Build tools: Upgrade to 0.12.2

This also changes `packageName` to `applicationId` per these
instructions:

http://tools.android.com/tech-docs/new-build-system/applicationid-vs-packagename
Fix index out of bounds error
Update spanish translation and translate public/private switch

Guide view: Fix edit on parts and tools

Any non-step page sould take you to edit guide details. This wasn't the
case for parts and tools which took you to edit the first step.

Guide completions: Use Api.getErrorDialog

It displays an appropriate error to the user and handles expired
sessions, retries, etc.

Guide completions: Consolidate ApiEvents

UncompleteGuide wasn't ever used so I decided to remove it.
Additionally, I changed CompleteGuide to be an ApiEvent<Boolean> so it
will work for uncompleting guides just like FavoriteGuide does.
Merge branch 'guide-completions' of github.com:iFixit/iFixitAndroid into guide-completions

Remove extra padding on all list views

It was causing problems everywhere.

Merge pull request #226 from iFixit/guide-completions

Guide completions and conclusion page
